==== Interventional Component (Metformin Trial)

    - Primary analysis: ANCOVA comparing HbA1c change and IL-6 change between metformin and placebo arms at 12 months, adjusted for baseline values
    - Secondary analysis: Cognitive function change (Montreal Cognitive Assessment) at 12 months
    - Subgroup analysis: Differential effect in patients with vs.\ without concurrent LDN
    - Adherence analysis: Association between metformin adherence and HbA1c/inflammatory improvements

